    <!-- Application Structure Plan: 
         1. Hero Section: High-level Definition & Status.
         2. Performance Dashboard: Quantitative Data (Latency/Cost) from Fig 1 & 6.
         3. Architecture Explorer: Interactive Diagram comparing Monolithic vs DTD (Fig 2 & 3).
         4. Logic Simulation: Interactive "Conflict Resolution" demo (Fig 4).
         5. Technical Specs & Domain Contact: Detailed Bio content and link to corepactai.com/dtdinfo.
         Rationale: Prioritizes the "Why" (Performance) and "How" (Architecture) before the "What" (Specs), easing the user into complex patent concepts.
    -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices:
         - Latency Chart: Bar Chart (Chart.js) -> Clear comparison of DTD vs Middleware vs Sequential.
         - Stream Simulation: HTML/CSS Animation -> Visualizes "Native Parallelization" without complex WebGL.
         - Logic Flow: Interactive State Machine -> Demonstrates "Learned Contextual Integration" (Fig 4) by letting users toggle conflict states.
         - Terminal: Scrolling Text Block -> Simulates the "Real-Time Execution Terminal" mentioned in the bio.
    -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
